Object-Factory-Declarative version 0.06
===============================

Object::Factory::Declarative - create object factories using declarative
syntax.

This module is a generalization of another class that managed the
loading and pre-initialization of HTML::Template files.  It provides
a simple way to declare and create object factory methods in any
arbitrary package.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Module::Build to build.

